  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety profiles of E6005 ointment
      in patients with atopic dermatitis compared to vehicle. The pharmacokinetic profile after
      topical application of E6005 is also assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
